						<div class="postbody">I like this idea.  iNES seems to work well enough, except for its redundant/lacking mapper descriptions, which this addresses nicely.  Would the $1A at the beginning also be updated?
<br />
<br />On the subject of rom formats, I always thought it would be a nice feature to keep battery-backed RAM within the rom file itself, so you don't have to copy .sav's from one emulator's folder to another.  Am I the only one who would like this?</div>

					
